<p>
<note n="0793b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0793b01">定善言此經乃修淨土之定善餘說淨土皆散善不及此也</note>
<note n="0794b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0794b01">其數與心等謂所得見之佛其佛之數與所念之佛正等</note>
<note n="0794b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0794b02">惟常念佛故常見佛</note>
<note n="0795b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0795b01">以下皆念佛普見法門</note>
<note n="0795b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0795b02">十回向位皆真向俗作度生功德故成佛時得具足功德之國土</note>
<note n="0796b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0796b01">稱佛當作佛此一乘大法何以故以念佛乃不生不滅空觀習如是觀者自然斷欲葢得禪定也</note>
<note n="0796b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0796b02">總前經緯本意述長行以結之</note>
</p>
